  "response": "\"I envy you\" is a phrase used to express that someone admires or feels a desire for something that another person has or experiences. It generally indicates that the speaker wishes they could have or experience that same thing. It can relate to various things such as qualities, possessions, situations, or opportunities that the other person enjoys or possesses.",
